docs.text: the story centres around a group of people , who include brit simon ( askew ) , and checkout girls claire ( holmes ) and ronna ( polley ) and the misadventures that they get into , split into three chapters .

docs.text: everything from sex to drugs to violence is covered in a film with a much blacker edge in comedy than swingers .

docs.text: although qt's touch is evident in nearly every frame , go is entertaining enough to forget about the similarities and just enjoy the rollercoaster ride .
